      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 11,
      "autoResize": true,
      "text": "Targets\n• <30s pipeline, <100ms queries\n\nDesign choices\n• Stream file reads\n• Bulk-load into SQLite staging tables\n• Transform in SQL (ELT)\n• Pure Python + Pydantic + FastAPI\n• Simple DI / testable layers",
      "originalText": "Targets\n• <30s pipeline, <100ms queries\n\nDesign choices\n• Stream file reads\n• Bulk-load into SQLite staging tables\n• Transform in SQL (ELT)\n• Pure Python + Pydantic + FastAPI\n• Simple DI / testable layers"
    },
