      "containerId": null,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 11,
      "autoResize": true,
      "text": "• ELT keeps heavy aggregation in SQL\n• GROUP BY flight_id + MAX() collapses events\n• Unknown equipment excluded from capacity\n• Validation errors are logged + skipped\n• Pipeline should be idempotent on re-run",
      "originalText": "• ELT keeps heavy aggregation in SQL\n• GROUP BY flight_id + MAX() collapses events\n• Unknown equipment excluded from capacity\n• Validation errors are logged + skipped\n• Pipeline should be idempotent on re-run"
    },
