      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 11,
      "autoResize": true,
      "text": "Batch (AWS)\nS3 → EventBridge → Step Functions → Lambda → Aurora → DynamoDB\n\nReal-time (Kafka)\nMinIO → Kafka → Consumers → PostgreSQL / Redis → Elasticsearch\n\nUse batch for large scheduled dumps; use Kafka for low-latency continuous ingestion.",
      "originalText": "Batch (AWS)\nS3 → EventBridge → Step Functions → Lambda → Aurora → DynamoDB\n\nReal-time (Kafka)\nMinIO → Kafka → Consumers → PostgreSQL / Redis → Elasticsearch\n\nUse batch for large scheduled dumps; use Kafka for low-latency continuous ingestion."
    },
